---
title: Veggie Sausages with Mushroom Redcurrant Jelly and Red Wine Stew and Mash
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Veggie Sausages with Mushroom & Mash in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-sausages-de6196bb-5ac27d5a.jpg
